Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaleido Star is about to begin. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nkeep your room brightly lit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Miss! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well now! Cathy here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you burning with youth, everybody?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let yourself go and get more\Nrevved up, push yourself higher!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everybody here is running\Nhead-on at his or her own dream!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Kaleido Stage is looking pretty good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! I've started to get revved up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna stick with you all like crazy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with this stage you've tried to protect!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:02.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the beginning\Nis red and black passions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:09.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, we rely on our contrary hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:16.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the last resort is a\Nmission which changes the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:24.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no place for\Nambiguous answers in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:32.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even while pretending not to\Nsee the impossible reality, we bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:38.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hard-to-obtain-truth\NCan you feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:42.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say to myself,\Nwho gets excited easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm confused about what to say {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:55.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' the never-waking\Ndream, the falling fate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:02.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:10.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, even\Nif I lose everything for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:17.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start the special training again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get on your feet.\NYou're wasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got so many weights on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been at it nonstop\Nsince early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she have to keep\Ngoing until she collapses like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can... keep going...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Our Amazing Futures."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon Park accepted the\Njob of writing the press copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, about Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of stopping Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the Angel's Maneuver\Nyou need innate instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Layla may not be able\Nto bring it off just by trying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And people are sure to pass judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on someone who leaves the stage and\Nthen comes back to make a second attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She made a brilliant exit,\Nbut this could sully it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean to make her give up on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to sully my own\Nreputation along with her, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the actual performance, I plan to use\Nlasers in those places where I've put film here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I think it's pretty good,\Nbut something's missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say flat-out that it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I wouldn't call it "no good"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying it's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's no good then, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to apologize, Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mia's the one at fault here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault, because I haven't completely\Nworked out how we'll stage the climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate we can't even build the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to give it my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Well said! Give it your best then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go at it like there's no tomorrow!\NGo at it until you collapse, like Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'll go at it until I collapse, like Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you want to move on this right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right... At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but please give Mia a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to give it a try...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seal loved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... was it was a success, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Odile can't express her love in\Nany other way but hating Odette...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then that means if she destroys Odette,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she won't be able to express love anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's like I was when I couldn't get pumped\Nup anymore because Sora had left the stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Odile is me... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the prince is to Odile {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is what the stage is to me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Odile can't win the prince's love as\Nlong as she keeps trying to defeat Odette.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The difference between Odette and Odile...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that Odile's love is the\Nmost important thing to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but on the other hand Odette values\Nthe prince more than she does herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora values the stage\Nmore than she does herself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I keep trying\Nto defeat Sora, I can't win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pose number nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The stage more than yourself, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora, don't tell me you're... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The training seems to involve\Nmore difficult things every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please wait one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, it's Mr. Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the wait. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting! Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is in the\Npractice room in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stubborn, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got no intention of\Nbecoming my partner, then go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To any outside observer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you making a comeback on the\NKaleido Stage doesn't look too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, they could even\Nget the impression you couldn't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you fail you'll be a laughingstock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what anyone thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do this. No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you're too wiped\Nout to even take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's that? Are you\Ntrying to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to change your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you... give me... a massage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this? Is this about right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not helping...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Thanks though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason this rankles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's a bar at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, we're going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks like this training\Nis going to be pretty harsh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintain your pose on the bar,\Nno matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of making my move\Nduring the climax a two-person move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already cleared it with Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing zoning out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get what I'm saying,\Nthen let's start practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you I wasn't\Ngoing to be in the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's got no hesitation about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine she'll go through with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it means she'll never\Nbe able to perform onstage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to the Kaleido Stage,\NMiss Layla wasn't here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even tell you how\Nbitterly disappointing that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The move that I'm thinking of\Nright now can't be done by one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm asking you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you refuse, I'll look for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you seriously want to\Ndo this thing, I'll train you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it. I want to give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her balance has improved, even if only a little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she doesn't own the pose\Nand her facial expression is strained.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's still not at a level\Nwhere she can take this onstage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Physically, I don't know if\NSora will last out this training...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a little change of scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where are we going at this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out when we get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seal seemed to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably better than nobody liking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real swans!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Mother Nature is the best stage director.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good for us to sit back\Nand be her audience sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get a firm image of an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel who doesn't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel who loves even her hating heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that suited Sora perfectly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too easy and perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though that probably sounds\Nfunny coming from me, since I wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm the same type as May.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charging headlong is more my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always made fun of\Npeople who said things like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's all get along and\Ndo this together as friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say, "You're just cowards\Nwho're afraid of getting hurt!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sora's different from them, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I tried to make her\Nbattle May, Sora refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May said she was just running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but those weren't the eyes of\Nsomeone who was running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of our regular players also\Nsay they can't sympathize with Sora
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when she says she won't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say "Come on, battle\NMay and show her a thing or two."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although those people\Nalways turn out to be the ones
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who don't have the courage to fight themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but that's about 80% of the\Npeople in this world, so it's a lost cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon pulled Sora onto the stage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gave a lively performance,\Nundaunted when May came after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something\Nreally thrilling about Sora then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't sense even a hint of the\Nweakness of someone who was running.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Sora's battling something, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe even inside Sora there's a\Nfear that the fighting may never stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's battling that fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sora hadn't made a\Nstage with no battles her goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe she couldn't have come\Nback to the Kaleido Stage when she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The force of the waves, the force\Nof the wind, the force of the boat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A lot of different forces are mixing together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's more complicated\Nthan the trapeze could ever be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sense the flow of all of\Nthe different forces at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think. Feel with your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you'll always be able to\Nreturn to your original position after you jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful not to break the pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Sora for you.\NShe's already on the right track.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lengths of the trapezes and the distances\Nbetween them are different than at Noir Circus,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can't use the same timing you did then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let your body relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's happening because\Nyou're not picturing your next move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:17:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your role is that of a fairy who guides me out\Nof the dark path of hatred I've wandered down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I have to express isn't hatred;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's Odile trying to defeat her own hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she has to get help from someone\Nwho will guide her with strong power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if my guide is that\Ntimid it ain't gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get this\Nbasic stuff over with fast
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and move on to the special\Ntraining for the Eternal Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eternal Illusion"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So close...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so my timing was too fast that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you got to this level on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good if I'm still thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to sense it directly with my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:18:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try changing the way you\Nchannel your strength each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it like this is the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this warms me up! Thanks, Miss Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave Japanese pork miso\Nsoup a try. I'm glad you like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame I'm so tired\Nthat I can't really taste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's too bad! And I felt\Npretty confident about it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried adding a bunch of fresh cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it nice? Is it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a good thing I can't really taste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Leon, do you want some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother Nature... Swans...\NThe Angel's Maneuver...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, this is too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I ran like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the seal would like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, the seal doesn't have to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is agony. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've started wanting to run away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like she's about at her limit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to run away when I was\Ntraining for the legendary great maneuver too,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because it hurt so bad. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason I could give it my all back then{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was because Miss Layla led me on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Miss Layla gave it her all right\Nthrough to the end just on her own power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without help from anyone. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Layla really is an amazing performer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should get better and better...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This show is gonna be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to come see it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I could meet the lead, Sora Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a fan of Sora's?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's been training at sea for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the true Angel's Manuever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like an angel... no, she {\i1}is {\i0}an angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just got an amazing idea. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only way to beat Sora\Nis to play the very best Odile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to make this show the very best show.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to make my dream\Ncome true on this stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone's hearts are starting to become one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leon, that's the stage of a true star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sophie, it looks like I'm finally going\Nto be able to keep my promise to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll practice more and more\Nright up until opening day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll make the true\NKaleido Star a reality no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another candidate\Nfor the role of Odette.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, we'll be holding an\Naudition for the role of Odette.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this "other candidate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contest is on, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, step down from your role.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:49.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All kinds of hard luck flocks\Nyour way as if it's spurring you on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:53.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swept away by it, time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:56.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as predicted, take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:00.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will get you out right away {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:02.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:04.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forcibly only (Drive with the fastest speed){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:08.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view I look down at every day is the best{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:10.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:15.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Escape for the sake of tomorrow {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:22.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I don't have a vacation, I've got an oasis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:29.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn off the cell phone and charge my love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:34.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because some pain,\Nyou can't soothe with just kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:38.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone, we pass each other by{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:39.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:45.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the far end of regret,\NI encounter my true heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:53.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether I'm crying or\Nlaughing, I will be with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:57.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Kaleido Star: New Wings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:24:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Back then, I never dreamed\Na day like this would come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm here because of my admiration for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your kindness, and your harshness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warmth we felt that day...\NI won't forget those things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at how much I've grown! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star,\N"A Most Amazing and Inescapable Showdown."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on towards the sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
